document_data.mainbody:
ezebel was the quasit familiar of Sylvira Savikas, one of the Great Readers of Candlekeep during the late 15 century DR.
She was rather mischievous and made Sylviras daily life just a bit more interesting, if a bit more disorderly.
Jezebel did not get along well with the hollyphant Lulu, when the celestial creature stayed in Candlekeep for a while.
